ed="T" n="0735c23"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0735c23"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName><persName key="A009412">禮宗</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0735c24"/><persName key="A009412">釋禮宗</persName>，俗姓宋，<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName>人也。道氣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g772"/>酋壯，志求玄<lb
ed="T" n="0735c25"/>微<ptr type="glossary" target="#g773"/>，願遂出塵，決除鞅絆。聞<placeName key="PL000000008801">長壽寺</placeName><ptr target="#n779"/>和尚通<lb
ed="T" n="0735c26"/>達禪觀，往叩其關，學習之心，未甞少懈。師<lb
ed="T" n="0735c27"/>誨<ref type="person" target="#A009412">之</ref>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009412">汝</ref>之出塵，有大利益，可謂良玉度<lb
ed="T" n="0735c28"/>尺，雖有十仞之土，不能揜其光矣。<ptr target="#n732"/>」乃奮<lb
ed="T" n="0735c29"/>藻攄華<ptr type="glossary" target="#g774"/>，注《涅槃經》，懷鉛握槧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g9"/>，周于二載。挫<pb ed="T" n="0736a" xml:id="T50.2061.0736a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0736a01"/>銳解紛，怡然理順，遂成夾注八十卷焉。及<lb
ed="T" n="0736a02"/><persName key="A009429">鄭卿</persName>尚書典郡<ptr target="#n781"/>，聞<ref type="person" target="#A009412">其</ref>盛名，致疏往請，確然<lb
ed="T" n="0736a03"/>拒而不赴。<date from-iso="0708-02-01" key="j19796821980065" to-iso="0709-02-18">景龍二年</date><ptr target="#n780"/>，有御史大夫<persName key="A009430">馮思</persName>忽爾<lb
ed="T" n="0736a04"/>暴終，入一處，有二童子持簿領<persName key="A009430">馮</persName>庭對判<lb
ed="T" n="0736a05"/>官廳，按覆<ptr type="glossary" target="#g775"/>罪愆，令望彼巨樹枝柯可覆數<lb
ed="T" n="0736a06"/>畝。判官身旁舊識者<persName key="A009431">張思義</persName>，招手呼<persName key="A009430">馮</persName>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0736a07"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A009431">吾</ref>是<ref type="person" target="#A009430">汝</ref>舅，曾為<placeName key="PL000000023581">洛陽</placeName>倉吏，被長官越格<ptr type="glossary" target="#g776"/>誣<lb
ed="T" n="0736a08"/>殺，兼假貸<placeName key="PL000000023592">太平寺</placeName>中錢及油麪，于今未脫。<lb
ed="T" n="0736a09"/><ref type="person" target="#A009430">汝</ref>所坐者，不合於<persName key="A002099">天后</persName>宮中亂越，致此暴<lb
ed="T" n="0736a10"/>卒。可發願造《涅<anchor xml:id="beg0736001"/>槃<anchor xml:id="end0736001"/>經》，鑄鐘。」登即關奏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g777"/>，判<lb
ed="T" n="0736a11"/>放却還人世。臨行，<persName key="A009431">張</persName>語<persName key="A009430">馮</persName>曰：「在閻浮<ptr type="glossary" target="#g778"/>一日<lb
ed="T" n="0736a12"/>造功德，得福無量，胡忍一生不修功德耶？<lb
ed="T" n="0736a13"/>此《涅槃經》者，<persName key="A009412">禮宗大師</persName>注解，從<ref type="person" target="#A001301">天台</ref>傳授，每<lb
ed="T" n="0736a14"/>有善神守護。」時<persName key="A009431">張</persName>差押<persName key="A009430">馮</persName>往諸司考校輕<lb
ed="T" n="0736a15"/>重生處，囑<persName key="A009430">之</persName>曰：「<persName key="A009430">汝</persName>去<placeName key="PL000000023561">洛城道光坊</placeName>內十字街<lb
ed="T" n="0736a16"/>第三宅是<persName key="A009431">吾</persName>家。家有池亭竹樹，為問妻兒<lb
ed="T" n="0736a17"/>安否？」<persName key="A009430">馮</persName>起，尋經本，未獲，而又死。經三日，立<lb
ed="T" n="0736a18"/>限歸，寫經鑄鐘<anchor xml:id="beg0736sgsz1"/>工<anchor xml:id="end0736sgsz1"/>畢。<persName key="A009430">馮</persName>在世得四十八年<lb
ed="T" n="0736a19"/>終。<persName key="A009412">宗</persName>亡，春秋九十七焉。</p>
